 of military bases and factories, the paper reported. Kim was seen limping in July during a TV appearance. \nThe paper said that Kim was still in the hospital, under heavy protection from bodyguards, and was receiving visits from several government officials.\nThis rumor seems to confirm what North Korean state media had said on Thursday, when state broadcaster Korean Central Television reported that Kim was \"not feeling well,\" and was suffering from an \"uncomfortable physical condition.\"","url":"https://mashable.com/2014/09/30/kim-jong-un-broke-ankles/","keywords":["north-korea","uncategorized","us-world","world","kim-jong-un"],"image":"https://mondrian.mashable.com/2014%252F09%252F30%252F64%252FKim_Un.e6925.jpg%252F950x534__filters%253Aquality%252880%2529.jpg","@type":"NewsArticle","mainEntityOfPage":"True","publisher":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Mashable","url":"https://mashable.com","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"/assets/mashable-publisher-logo-d1800cc5b71606b40182307b4f7158b5dbb17dee6b9c4b612a40c0be40c60bbc.png","width":"357","height":"60"}},"thumbnailUrl":"https://mondrian.mashable.com/2014%252F09%252F30%252F64%252FKim_Un.e6925.jpg%252F205x115__filters%253Aquality%252880%2529.jpg","dateCreated":"2014-09-30T18:26:27.000Z","datePublished":"2014-09-30T18:26:27.000Z","author":"Lorenzo Franceschi-Bicchierai","creator":"Lorenzo Franceschi-Bicchierai","dateModified":"2014-09-30T18:26:44.371Z","articleSection":"World"}</script><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Organization","name":"Mashable","url":"https://mashable.com","potentialAction":{"@type":"SearchAction","target":"https://www.mashable.com/search/?query={search_term_string}","query-input":"required name=search_term_string"},"logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"/assets/mashable-publisher-logo-d1800cc5b71606b40182307b4f7158b5dbb17dee6b9c4b612a40c0be40c60bbc.png","width":"357","height":"60"},"sameAs":["https://www.facebook.com/mashable/","https://twitter.com/